    {
      "id": "N9wEYVuGbwxqx59LTzLt0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2021.1806512301741,
      "y": -14014.374568726986,
      "width": 1144.33154296875,
      "height": 720,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6Z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 680872813,
      "version": 956,
      "versionNonce": 1739212720,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767965503319,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "All Of them are independent running on different\nserver, we can choose diff diff languse of these\nevery service is responsible for a dedicated service\nor functiionality.\nEvery service can be deployed independently\nevey servide can be scaled independently \n\nIn monolyth these code can easily communicate like\na function call because everything on a single codebase\n\nIn Microservice if these services want to communicate\nthey communicate via some network calls (REST, GRPC, GraphQl)\n\nBest part about Microservice is because we have individual \nproject actually having diff modules the overall code management\nbecomes relatively very easy we have small codebases to manage.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "All Of them are independent running on different\nserver, we can choose diff diff languse of these\nevery service is responsible for a dedicated service\nor functiionality.\nEvery service can be deployed independently\nevey servide can be scaled independently \n\nIn monolyth these code can easily communicate like\na function call because everything on a single codebase\n\nIn Microservice if these services want to communicate\nthey communicate via some network calls (REST, GRPC, GraphQl)\n\nBest part about Microservice is because we have individual \nproject actually having diff modules the overall code management\nbecomes relatively very easy we have small codebases to manage.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
